	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=242843><span id= >ZaxxHatebringer</span></a><br><span id=notbold>7 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Yah Ive tried that, but nobody seems to buy them. Anything else maybe? Right now Im trying to get mammoth tusks in Everfrost, but hard to find the mammoths.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p>&nbsp;<br>Zaxx Hatebringer<br>51 Cleric of Innoruuk<br>Firiona Vie<br><br>Finamor<br>30 Warrior of Rallos Zek<br>Karana</td></td></tr>
